Government Circular, Water Supply and Sanitation Department, No: Apna-0224 / Q. No.19 / Papu-15 dated 10.01.2024

The General Administration Department has issued a comprehensive policy as per the notification No. 1 in this regard for the preparation and publication of merit lists of officers / employees of the government service every year. The tentative merit list dated 01.01.2024 for the category "Assistant Administrative Officer (Group-B)" in Ground Water Surveillance and Development System under reference No.2 was published. Taking into account the objections received in this regard, a provisional final report showing the status of the Assistant Administrative Officer (Group-B) category in the Ground Water Surveillance and Development System as on 01.01.2024 has been prepared.
